casebody.data:
Andrew J. Di Paola et al., Respondents, v. City of Glen Cove et al., Appellants. Submitted September 28, 1964; decided October 1, 1964. Melvin H. Heiko, City Attorney, for appellants.

No one opposed.

Motion dismissed, with $10 costs, upon the ground that the order sought to be appealed from does not finally determine the action within the meaning of the Constitution.
